{"tid":834240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【高鐵首日未達標】昨日7.6萬人次經西九出入境　佔總數7%","createTime":"2018-09-24T05:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T02:26:11.000Z","uid":195944,"like":170,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0d3434226ec6c35a590c6d4de70165c0dee07a","tid":834240,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180924/s00001/1537748092820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F1537748092820&d=TdIywUwWg4I4fsrcBNr70MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=27c812cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F1537748092820&h=67e53ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180924/s00001/1537748092820</a><br />\n<br />\n耗資逾844億元的廣深港高鐵香港段昨日通車。政府早前已將預測日均客流量大幅下調至8萬，惟根據入境處臨時數字，昨日首日通車入境及出境人次僅75,517，未達目標。<br />\n<br />\n根據入境管制站昨日旅客抵港及離境臨時數字，共有571,707人次入境及508,274人次出境，即共有1,079,981人次。其中經高鐵西九龍站出入境人次75,517（入境42,509 / 出境33,008），僅佔總人次約7%。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最多人經羅湖出入境，達307,703人次；其次是落馬洲支線的198,584人次；經機場出入境的則有134,974人次。<br />\n<br />\n第一日趁新屎坑都無八萬人 仲要係星期日有中秋節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前仲話十一萬人次 <br />\n<br />\n真係算命呃你十年八年 政府想呃都呃唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55628652d95b822b80aa6f21319bcfd16fa2fe1","tid":834240,"uid":70786,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"大好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3b92aed22226318ba755a2fe5584735927208a","tid":834240,"uid":8048,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"篤數好辛苦㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd454bb179bb18ca2bc3e291ba32721154965cf9","tid":834240,"uid":6752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"新屎坑咋仲要"},{"pid":"2d840b69a42c4771c218a1390f18df3911aa03fc","tid":834240,"uid":108347,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"肯定係啲人怕迫唔一早迫去搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實冇所謂，最緊要係個經濟效益同發展機遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd201b93be772642fa3b2b622057a89c8bbe795","tid":834240,"uid":195944,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"呀地中海局長 你要唔要將個人次再減下 減到得翻你啲頭髮嘅數量就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da30d1195c533b91802d342aedb4fb2689a3d917","tid":834240,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9fd201b93be772642fa3b2b622057a89c8bbe795","tid":834240,"uid":195944,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"呀地中海局長 你要唔要將個人次再減下 減到得翻你啲頭髮嘅數量就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/d